questionsAndAnswers.question:
Have the store hours changed? I came here during there posted open hours and they were closed.
Love this place, just wanted to have the correct store hours for future visits.

answers.answer: They are open from 8am to 7 pm Monday thru Friday and Saturday 9am to 1 pm
